{"tid":2387967,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日先知GME 個遊戲點玩 [第一個gif]","createTime":"2021-01-30T17:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T19:46:20.000Z","uid":93050,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fd174899f9d8376e0d79888997781b5e415ca42f","tid":2387967,"uid":93050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T17:29:05.000Z","msg":"遊戲玩法：<br />\n1. Mark 實條紅色線 （price）： 做長倉條紅線低過你買入價就輸；做短倉條紅線高過你賣出價你就輸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0zP7k9R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0zP7k9R.png&h=82e29bf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 將紅線推向敵方：咁樣先賺到錢<br />\n3. 假設玩家都會<span class=\"xx-large\">止損</span>： <br />\n3.1 做長倉輸太多就會平倉，<strong>賣</strong>出股票，加入空軍<br />\n3.2 做短倉輸太多就會平倉，<strong>買</strong>入股票<br />\n<br />\n大戶/高手一般可以借股票再賣比其他人（股票嘅supply就會大過demand，價格下跌），大戶跟住就係低位買返啲股票，再還返俾人。<br />\n一般人都會低買高賣，做short 就會高賣低買，分別就在於買同賣嘅順序顛倒左<br />\n<br />\n收割散戶嘅方法： 大大力咁借股票再沽空，散戶見到形勢凶險就會走，大戶就買返散戶嘅股票。<br />\n4. 以下係大戶收割散戶嘅示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wViPzxe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwViPzxe.gif&h=e5ff9547&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係如果大戶賣左股票，股價大升，就要局住買返啲股票還比人。<br />\n要收割大戶，<span class=\"xx-large\">方法</span>就係 1. 號召更多人買 2. SH lock 死啲貨 3. 大戶見無貨就會bid 高個價 4. 股價繼續破新高 5. 繼續令更多做短倉嘅人<strong>輸</strong>錢 6. loop 落去。<br />\n<br />\n5. 散戶收割大戶嘅示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kyJLSjx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkyJLSjx.gif&h=20359fd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7eb5e6d494c1fc6be3aabfa43e241266656ebd9b","tid":2387967,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T17:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad5348ee825919a255d8edd587bb9376058798b","tid":2387967,"uid":122083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T17:34:52.000Z","msg":"兩個連登仔最尾先進場？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b133d3ac23cb6dfc2c897cc2e9103571e402ff4","tid":2387967,"uid":93050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ad5348ee825919a255d8edd587bb9376058798b","tid":2387967,"uid":122083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T17:34:52.000Z","msg":"兩個連登仔最尾先進場？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T17:36:11.000Z","msg":"連登仔跟Reddit 同wsb"},{"pid":"5f0d0dd6338ef68ecd14893f2a8242b510438700","tid":2387967,"uid":95520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T19:46:20.000Z","msg":"咁有心機幫你推推"}]}